sequenceDiagram
    participant Host as Host or GPU client
    participant Bridge as PCIe or NoC bridge
    participant NoC
    participant MC as Memory Controller
    participant MEM as VRAM
    participant DVFS as DVFS FSM

    DVFS->>NoC: block memory ingress
    DVFS->>MC: wait outstanding drain
    Host->>Bridge: VRAM read request
    Bridge->>NoC: request reaches ingress
    NoC-->>Bridge: backpressure or no credit
    Bridge->>Bridge: queue request
    MC-->>DVFS: outstanding == 0
    DVFS->>MEM: enter safe memory state
    DVFS->>MC: switch memory OPP
    MC-->>DVFS: memory ready
    DVFS->>NoC: unblock memory ingress
    Bridge->>NoC: issue queued read
    NoC->>MC: read request
    MC->>MEM: read command
    MEM-->>MC: data
    MC-->>Bridge: data
    Bridge-->>Host: read response or PCIe completion
